ef44ee7d.original:
This method makes a database backup. This method abstracts the
[`sqlite3_backup_init()`](https://www.sqlite.org/c3ref/backup_finish.html#sqlite3backupinit),
[`sqlite3_backup_step()`](https://www.sqlite.org/c3ref/backup_finish.html#sqlite3backupstep)
and [`sqlite3_backup_finish()`](https://www.sqlite.org/c3ref/backup_finish.html#sqlite3backupfinish) functions.

The backed-up database can be used normally during the backup process. Mutations coming from the same connection - same
`DatabaseSync` - object will be reflected in the backup right away. However, mutations from other connections will cause
the backup process to restart.

```js
import { backup, DatabaseSync } from 'node:sqlite';

const sourceDb = new DatabaseSync('source.db');
const totalPagesTransferred = await backup(sourceDb, 'backup.db', {
  rate: 1, // Copy one page at a time.
  progress: ({ totalPages, remainingPages }) => {
    console.log('Backup in progress', { totalPages, remainingPages });
  },
});

console.log('Backup completed', totalPagesTransferred);
```

ef44ee7d.translated:
このメソッドはデータベースのバックアップを作成する。このメソッドは [`sqlite3_backup_init()`](https://www.sqlite.org/c3ref/backup_finish.html#sqlite3backupinit)・[`sqlite3_backup_step()`](https://www.sqlite.org/c3ref/backup_finish.html#sqlite3backupstep)・[`sqlite3_backup_finish()`](https://www.sqlite.org/c3ref/backup_finish.html#sqlite3backupfinish) 関数を抽象化する。

バックアップされるデータベースは、バックアップ処理中も通常どおり使える。同じ接続(同じ `DatabaseSync` オブジェクト)から来る変更は、すぐにバックアップに反映される。ただし、他の接続からの変更はバックアップ処理を再起動させる。

```js
import { backup, DatabaseSync } from 'node:sqlite';

const sourceDb = new DatabaseSync('source.db');
const totalPagesTransferred = await backup(sourceDb, 'backup.db', {
  rate: 1, // Copy one page at a time.
  progress: ({ totalPages, remainingPages }) => {
    console.log('Backup in progress', { totalPages, remainingPages });
  },
});

console.log('Backup completed', totalPagesTransferred);
```

